| Term          | Simple Meaning              | Example                   |
| ------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Node          | Element in the tree         | A, B, C                   |
| Root          | Topmost node                | A                         |
| Parent        | Node with children          | A                         |
| Child         | Node below a parent         | B                         |
| Sibling       | Same parent                 | B and C                   |
| Leaf Node     | No children                 | D, E, F                   |
| Internal Node | Has at least one child      | A, B, C                   |
| Degree        | Number of children          | Degree(A) = 2             |
